{"tid":969250,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離屋好似傳出酸臭味, 駛唔駛報驚","createTime":"2019-01-05T02:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T11:45:51.000Z","uid":4349,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e5cd94984737e839c2fdb3a6b9f49e0bb3bc1a","tid":969250,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"由琴晚放工番屋企就聞到一陣好強烈酸臭咸魚味, CHECK哂成屋都無味源<br />\n後來CONFIRM係由窗口傳入, 窗口對面係隔離屋<br />\n即刻開門出去好似狗咁索隔離屋道門縫位, 又好似無咩味<br />\n今日起身陣味仲係到, 係窗口位飄過黎<br />\n<br />\n講開隔離屋長期無人, 係有個阿伯得閒番黎一陣, 之後又走, 未見過有人過夜<br />\n門口長期用報紙封住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過報紙爛左, 個阿伯留黎又封好佢<br />\n<br />\n我今晚番去仲聞到陣味既話, 睇黎都要報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead8537e2f938749d1b1acb6129a962cd5da551e","tid":969250,"uid":24121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c59ecda6708323ac1401c86f21b6fbdb18b36ed7","tid":969250,"uid":200595,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"報保安"},{"pid":"7abef33e8dfa9e078b39d7133bc12635de4d4196","tid":969250,"uid":5967,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"叫車<br />\n報臭味，懷疑氣體洩漏<br />\n之後會上齊黎嫁啦"},{"pid":"b660b4f7310497478cea76483d09e29d3fd2c201","tid":969250,"uid":127118,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:10:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗 見有蟲走出來先報都未遲"},{"pid":"c283b52063aad424c9747570e138f5b618b9efc3","tid":969250,"uid":31758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b660b4f7310497478cea76483d09e29d3fd2c201","tid":969250,"uid":127118,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:10:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗 見有蟲走出來先報都未遲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7196f9ec6defe76b18714029d3e3e60de2ac8cbb","tid":969250,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,